{"tid":871442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免費激光去肚紋 80後女子2級燒傷","createTime":"2018-10-22T02:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T09:17:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c495d5b305f4fc27c71f7987f7c291a60e1c57c0","tid":871442,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】一名80後女子上月在美容院介紹下，免費在肚皮接受CO2激光療程去除肚紋，疑因儀器公司職員疏忽造成肚皮滲血紅腫致2級燒傷，或永久留疤。協助事主的民主黨促港府盡快就規管醫療儀器立法，並同時要求操作者負上責任。<br />\n<br />\n約30歲陳小姐（化名）上月初經美容院東主介紹免費在肚皮接受CO2激光療程，由醫療儀器公司職員操作儀器，美容院東主從旁督導。美容院及儀器公司均僅向事主稱最多只會「起痧」，沒讓事主簽下療程同意書。她憶述，療程期間感灼熱和痛楚5至10分鐘，她曾要求暫停及詢問是否需注射麻醉藥，卻被游說只需「忍一下」，惟完成後，其肚皮出現滲血及紅腫，被建議塗抹聲稱促進康復的藥膏。<br />\n<br />\n疑職員操作不當用錯度數<br />\n惟她懷疑職員操作不當及用錯能量度數，向3名專科醫生求醫後，被診斷為2級燒傷，或永久留疤。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨醫療政策副發言人袁海文表示，儀器公司及美容院拒承認責任，反指事主處理傷口不當，將助事主向儀器公司法律追討因疏忽所造成傷害的損失，又促食衞局重新規管醫學美容儀器使用者，並設全面醫療事故呈報制度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DuAqIoZj94VnOAg1EFpXcA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/20181022JHC001__20181022_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDuAqIoZj94VnOAg1EFpXcA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F20181022JHC001__20181022_L.jpg&h=af698266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IzQ6.iSqr51OwLr2LZ1_Kw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/20181022JHC003__20181022_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIzQ6.iSqr51OwLr2LZ1_Kw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F20181022JHC003__20181022_L.jpg&h=d9d7065e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JtT7muTQKouhzDWYbwkTeA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9Mjk4O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/014_01_a_20181022_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJtT7muTQKouhzDWYbwkTeA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9Mjk4O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F014_01_a_20181022_L.jpg&h=43f15942&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44054c58a6acce06deededb834fdaa9930198e92","tid":871442,"uid":1487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"見到都覺痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd81f8986beba742a3794813dc542cf8e6bce69f","tid":871442,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:37:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5311f724fa5420f6842b8b10fbbd95e5882f67a4","tid":871442,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bW6xMAy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbW6xMAy.gif&h=8b617e80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40a7f6d8fdbb00af792d48704e39e916ca8f2b2f","tid":871442,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44054c58a6acce06deededb834fdaa9930198e92","tid":871442,"uid":1487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"見到都覺痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4953d8c2354dce1de8b551ff092057f41d10496f","tid":871442,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:13:22.000Z","msg":"免費真係貴"},{"pid":"ffc6662f55a5caae75566708844a63f956671f90","tid":871442,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"可唔可以再做另一次激光去疤"},{"